{"tid":420514,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King’s Raid #17 10月2日中秋活動開跑(免費專武劵)","createTime":"2017-10-01T12:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T12:54:23.000Z","uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d40382db5e17a6164959772aec79f83bfe3a62b9","tid":420514,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Sever【Asia】</span></strong></span><br />\n需入公會嘅巴絲請留言提供ID，謝謝合作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/204618_be489187f7143ee02f5231916e99e451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F204618_be489187f7143ee02f5231916e99e451.jpg&h=204a42c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKing`s Raid(簡稱KR)<br />\n橫向類型遊戲<br />\n戰鬥畫面打擊感強，角色精美<br />\n技能、職業種類多各有用途<br />\n玩家可以組合屬於自己既隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174135_9c2624011a20e6ecbc02e0c14535660d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174135_9c2624011a20e6ecbc02e0c14535660d.jpg&h=7fb1cbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ANDROID</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F4943&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b5d771f\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IOS</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fkings-raid%2Fid1097735195&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=626f31c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195</a><br />\n已經收到由 香港 巴打提供嘅美國AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如有需要借用可以聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King's Raid 新手入門【By湯丸】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 各職專武繁中翻譯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 全人物覺醒表 v1.2【繁中版】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 英雄評價表【連登版】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【King&rsquo;s Raid】 各英詳細介紹表(包括技能T1-5點法、裝備屬性、符文等)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 2,3,5星券揀咩角色好呀?(5星為活動券,通常係活動期間登入夠7日就有,每日重置時間為香港時間零晨1點)<br />\nA:隊形一般會選擇1坦2輸出1奶<br />\n2星券,<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框為首選</span>(Gau係戰士,可做坦可做物理輸出,Kaulah為牧師,用途較廣)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174055_47837c961a4a610cdb7ecfcaf1525ed2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174055_47837c961a4a610cdb7ecfcaf1525ed2.jpg&h=d1d0a8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3星券,<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框為冇活動5星券既首選DPS</span>,<span style=\"color: purple;\">紫框為有活動5星券首選多控場副DPS</span>,<span style=\"color: green;\">綠框為有活動5星券可選角色</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174021_7ac5652dda98c56113ef53421a28a573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174021_7ac5652dda98c56113ef53421a28a573.jpg&h=9c6f8b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5星券,<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框為首選DPS</span>,<span style=\"color: green;\">綠框為次選DPS</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/182455_ca39beb218941c55b59be1f9b18bd2c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F182455_ca39beb218941c55b59be1f9b18bd2c4.jpg&h=58227264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講就講曬,仲有選擇困難既就問你自己細佬啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ:咁其他角色呢?唔揀係咪即係廢?<br />\nA:唔係,大部分角色都有各自既用途同玩法,有D係打龍勁,有D係PVP勁,有D係打BOSS勁,有D係推圖勁,仲有分前期角同後期角,不過玩耐左就會明,只係開頭揀勁既DPS黎用姐<br />\n<br />\nQ:我個隊應該點配呀?<br />\nA:一隊入面一般配置就係1坦2輸出1奶,其中一個輸出會係拎黎控場(控場技能即係CC)用既副DPS,因為控場可以打斷敵人既技能,例如係敵人吟唱時間你暈佢,佢就冇得出依招技,係PVP黎講甚至會令對手冇埋Mana(Mana=出技cost),進而令你較容易獲勝<br />\n<br />\nQ：需唔需要刷首抽架？<br />\nA：冇首抽依回事，角色可以用自選卷,用石買同係酒館到溝返黎，專武就每日免費抽都有機會中<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩英好用？<br />\nＡ：評價表：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/KRzAey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FKRzAey&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=38ee6b63\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/KRzAey</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YfHeybcKj3R3Qq6Tzg1nJFiH9OYAcOxHD3WIJxBhrPk/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1YfHeybcKj3R3Qq6Tzg1nJFiH9OYAcOxHD3WIJxBhrPk%2Fedit&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7ad952ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YfHeybcKj3R3Qq6Tzg1nJFiH9OYAcOxHD3WIJxBhrPk/edit</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：D武器裝備點搞啊？點分？<br />\nA：專武T10(得武器有專武 - 一開始會送男劍專武一把)<br />\n金(RAID/商店金抽/紅石抽)<br />\n紅(主線HARD/HELL MODE/RAID/商店金抽/紅石抽)<br />\n紫(主線HARD/HELL MODE/RAID/商店金抽/紅石抽)<br />\n藍(分解)<br />\n綠白(分解)<br />\n<br />\nQ：卡主線點搞？<br />\nA：試下睇一次自動打，咩原因卡先<br />\n如果喺唔夠力嘅就升下角升下裝<br />\n如果喺死喺Boss出技嘅話可以等隻王出技嘅時候出CC技斷佢<br />\n<br />\nQ：幾LV封頂？<br />\nＡ：80，英雄1至80級所需經驗 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZTSaJj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZTSaJj&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4e4306a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZTSaJj</a><br />\n<br />\n如有更多問題可詳見【LIHKG】King's Raid 新手入門【By湯丸】或回覆<br />\n即有專人回答您<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9032203dc8b4891f734817634f3372ad7dcdb4d5","tid":420514,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>囡囡J圖吸客區</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/213342_b99b2f2f055437a55e0cab7f23f514fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F213342_b99b2f2f055437a55e0cab7f23f514fe.jpg&h=6ef6883a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/213350_7c75c9dead258cad8cd6ef2dbc39a6db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F213350_7c75c9dead258cad8cd6ef2dbc39a6db.jpg&h=c7d06d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/213359_e7345700406bf1cf4d2a44ccbbba8c33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F213359_e7345700406bf1cf4d2a44ccbbba8c33.jpg&h=fcd5e9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">仔仔J圖吸客區</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174805_a47fa265a39d13989cf2c72d8c59d14a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174805_a47fa265a39d13989cf2c72d8c59d14a.jpg&h=445c8f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174743_88a69e365737debbff11c57785383c06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174743_88a69e365737debbff11c57785383c06.jpg&h=942e67b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174748_00bcba74c7dfba53fb3e2ed36faa9b2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174748_00bcba74c7dfba53fb3e2ed36faa9b2f.jpg&h=6015105b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>人外J圖吸客區</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174839_c72e4e9de297804e211fafa10f015290.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174839_c72e4e9de297804e211fafa10f015290.jpg&h=4cb37a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174844_0815e732bb868667293a5797b98a252b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174844_0815e732bb868667293a5797b98a252b.jpg&h=1a9c9bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/174848_c5f87788921150b2bcd3917068aa8147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F174848_c5f87788921150b2bcd3917068aa8147.jpg&h=6a4a1aab&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2912c8b49d6995ef91174fcda8a3fff49a68f1dc","tid":420514,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>迎中秋活動<br />\n10月2日維護後 ~ 10月15日 24:00</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/203507_4b87f2fc074f0ee279f1f7a086203bed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F203507_4b87f2fc074f0ee279f1f7a086203bed.jpg&h=4c77767a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動內容: 收集鬆糕兌換禮物<br />\n<br />\n- 普通副本隨機掉落0~5個鬆糕<br />\n- 完成龍raid可隨機獲得0~5個鬆糕<br />\n- 消耗10個鑽石可獲得1個鬆糕, 消耗鑽石最多可獲得1500個鬆糕<br />\n*難度越高的普通副本掉率越高, BOSS副本掉率更高<br />\n*龍副本掉率高於普通副本<br />\n*適用戰利品雙倍獲得券<br />\n*消耗鑽石不能獲得鬆糕的項目有符文拆卸/詞綴重置/刷新商店/材料本,討伐戰,地牢,競技場重置/快速製作材料/背包擴充<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/203508_5cfc9067ae5c33dfe4727d911c718a5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F203508_5cfc9067ae5c33dfe4727d911c718a5f.jpg&h=f8302bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可兌換獎勵<br />\n25個鬆糕 中秋禮物盒 x1 (不限)<br />\n100個鬆糕 中級附魔箱 x1 (限10次)<br />\n300個鬆糕 無限之石 x1 (限3次)<br />\n900個鬆糕 遺物碎片 x1000 (限1次)<br />\n900個鬆糕 隨機專武獲得券 x1 (限1次)<br />\n*打開中級附魔箱可隨機獲得珍稀~古代的附魔捲軸<br />\n*打開中秋禮物盒可隨機獲得金幣/魔法粉/技能書/不知名碎片/不知名符文/各種鑰匙/各種雙倍券/體力/隨機專武(除了梅伊)<br />\n<br />\n中秋禮物盒 可兌換獎勵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/203508_c5b3baa843ca94abfffa1eeb12463c5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F203508_c5b3baa843ca94abfffa1eeb12463c5b.png&h=d9ff2531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n*獎勵通過郵件發放<br />\n*未兌換的鬆糕將在活動結束後消失<br />\n活動原文：<a href=\"https://www.plug.game/kingsraid-en/events#/posts/4036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plug.game%2Fkingsraid-en%2Fevents%23%2Fposts%2F4036&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8c327f75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.plug.game/kingsraid-en/events#/posts/4036</a><br />\n活動翻譯：<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12539313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12539313&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=82613bd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12539313</a></div>"},{"pid":"3dae603eecaccc16d1fe389b1f46c8708e1341ef","tid":420514,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a29f2524199015779dec85cc51364a638155e33","tid":420514,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"換左aisha升星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b1c4abb91d9496dbfa9eccafbe0183d82da6f7","tid":420514,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"新POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/420511/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/420511/page/1</a>"}]}